Task3:
    
    Get one string from user
    
    a = "computer"
    
    convert middle character to upper case
    
    a = "computer" ==> compUter
    groovyy ==> groOvyy
    
    
    

Code:
    
a = input("Enter the string:\n")
mid = int(len(a)/2)
print(a[:mid]+ a[mid].upper()+ a[mid+1:])   
    


Output:
 
